OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud across
OL,6,Fthe north and west will drift
OL,7,Feastwards through the evening and may
OL,8,Fresult in low cloud or sea fog along
OL,9,Fwestern coasts and murky conditions
OL,10,Fover hills. Potential for a little
OL,11,Frain in places.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA cooler and more changeable
OL,14,Fday, with a band of patchy rain moving
OL,15,Feastwards at first. Clearing in the
OL,16,Fafternoon leaving sunny spells and
OL,17,Fblustery showers. Feeling cooler than
OL,18,Ftoday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
